---
title: Silky Sicilian Chicken Sausage Penne  tossed with Mushrooms, Zucchini & Tomatoes
description: Web Description: Mad for mushrooms? The fab fungi is the backbone of this pasta recipe along with rich mushroom stock, bringing all those deep, earthy flavors that you know and love. We’ve added al dente penne, zucchini, tomatoes, a lemony, chive-flecked crème fraîche sauce, and a sprinkling of Parmesan cheese. Get ready for this umami-packed dish to hit your dinner table.
